SUMMARY:Urban Harvest Farmers Market
DTSTAMP:20260623T142731Z
DTSTART:20260627T130000Z
DESCRIPTION:Nonprofit Saturday farmers market with local produce\, food\, a
	nd garden vendors.\n\nhttps://www.urbanharvest.org/events/\n\nFrom Urban H
